rows.label: qev025704_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh, a human! I find you all very very fascinating, no?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0002
rows.name: I'm happy to talk for as long as you like, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_SEL0021
rows.name: Find out why Vyponne is so interested in humans.

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0003
rows.name:
Oh! You're here on an errand for my daughter, are
you now? And just what has Panyar gotten herself into
this time?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0004
rows.name:
...Collaborating with humans to make underwear?
Most most fascinating![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0005
rows.name:
Of course I'll help in any way I can, won't I?
If you don't mind staying right there for a moment,
I'll go measure myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0006
rows.name: Here you are! Straight from my body to yours, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0007
rows.name:
Will we Ma-non all start dressing in human-style
clothes from now on, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0008
rows.name:
Well, I can't wait. Tell my darling girl to to to keep up
the good work, won't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0009
rows.name:
Unlike we Ma-non, humans wear all manner of unique
clothing, don't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0010
rows.name:
They're all so so lovely and most most entertaining to
look at! I hope I have the chance to try them on for
myself one day?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0011
rows.name:
I think I'm most looking forward to trying on a set of
underwear for myself one day?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0012
rows.name:
Please tell my daughter I wish her the best of luck,
all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0013
rows.name: Panyar sent word to me straightaway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0014
rows.name:
She said underwear is terribly restricting.
I believe the term she used was "body shackles"?
Isn't that dreadful?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025704_MSG0015
rows.name:
I can only imagine the deep and pervasive tragedies
of human history that led to such customs taking root.[ST:wait ]
